    <main>
      <h1 class="hidden" id="pageTitle">Through The Veil</h1>

      <p class="hidden" id="line1">
        You found it.
      </p>
       
      <p class="hidden" id="line2">
        Some things are meant to be stepped into.
      </p>

       <a
        href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GCM12FFJ"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="button hidden"
        id="amazonBtn"
        onclick="window.uetq=window.uetq||[];window.uetq.push('event','AmazonClick',{}); if(typeof gtag==='function'){gtag('event','conversion',{'send_to':'AW-988775825/84DWCLnc3f0BEJGIVtcd'});}">
        Click to Read Free on Kindle Unlimited or Buy Now on Amazon
      </a>

      <p class="hidden blurb" id="blurb">
        A veil—hidden in plain sight—separates Light from Dark on our own world.
        
        Cole Hunter doesn’t find it by accident.
        He soon learns he was drawn to it.
        
        Crossing it was easy. Coming back… isn’t.
        
        The life he knew—his wife, Anna… his dog, Dallas—remains on the other side, while every path home pulls him deeper into a realm of predators, power, and consequences that cannot be undone.
        
        Soon, Cole realizes something worse than being trapped—
        leaving may not be an option.
        
        Because the fate of countless souls now rests on his shoulders.
        
        Faced with a choice between returning to the life he loves or standing against the horrors consuming this world…
        
        Cole makes the only choice that matters.
        
        He stays.
        And he fights.
      </p>      
        
       <p class="hidden" id="line3"> 
        Not everything is meant to be explained right away.
      </p>

      <p class="hidden genre" id="genreLine"> 
        A Fast Paced, Gritty Supernatural Thriller — You Won't Be Able To Put Down
      </p>

      <a
        href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GCM12FFJ"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
